snippet: Emmanuel Sanders, formerly of the Pittsburgh Steelers, is the fifth high-profile player signed by Denver in this off-season.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Denver Broncos sign free agent wide receiver Emmanuel Sanders to a three-year, $15 million contract; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Emmanuel Sanders, formerly of the Pittsburgh Steelers, is the fifth high-profile player signed by Denver in this off-season.

headline.main: Receiver Sanders Joins the Broncos’ Free-Agency Haul
headline.print_headline: Sanders, a Receiver, Joins Denver’s Free-Agency Haul
